@host = http://localhost:5105

### Submit a payment (70% failure rate — will retry 3x then dead-letter)
POST {{host}}/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 99.99,
  "currency": "PLN"
}

### Get all failed (dead-lettered) payments
GET {{host}}/payments/failed

### Health check
GET {{host}}/health
